<div class="center-down text-center">
	<br/></br>
	Mokkalog is the platform to discover independent, innovative, underrated, and unique fashion brands.
	<br/><br/>
	Mokkalog has a huge collection with variety of genre of brands, we promise you will find something you love.
	<br/></br>
	Mokkalog is an open platform which means any brand owners can list their brand. Our moderators are working hard to clean up the listings, but please be careful when visiting outside links.
	<br/><br/>
